{"tid":988561,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【單身福利】返工太忙無時間拍拖？杭州中學為單身老師設「戀愛假」！","createTime":"2019-01-20T07:37:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-20T07:40:27.000Z","uid":212399,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"325411883f26d23c1faac1547456eb1b0da3101d","tid":988561,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T07:37:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/techstart.presslogic.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Love525.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com%2Ftechstart.presslogic.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F01%2FLove525.jpg&h=42c13f92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n經常話「個個都拍拖」，唔通個個都有拖拍？浙江杭州市丁蘭實驗中學昨日（15日）宣布，單身的年輕教師和已婚未生子的老師均可享有「戀愛假」，只要沒有影響課程編排和教學，符合條件的老師每月可以上網申請兩次「戀愛假」，每次不超過半日，希望有助他們能在生活和工作之間取得平衡。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/techstart.presslogic.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/bkn-20190116144732214-0116_00952_001_01b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com%2Ftechstart.presslogic.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F01%2Fbkn-20190116144732214-0116_00952_001_01b.jpg&h=d9ce2c03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n該中學早已有「獨子假」的傳統，讓老師可以抽身照顧家中的孩子，也可送孩子上培訓班、參加親子活動。內地政府取消「一孩政策」後，愈來愈多老師育有兩名小孩，於是校方將「獨子假」升級為「親子假」，為老師提供更多福利。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/techstart.presslogic.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/hWOd-hrsechc5542947.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com%2Ftechstart.presslogic.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F01%2FhWOd-hrsechc5542947.jpg&h=b526aca5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n此外，因部分老師的孩子已經長大成人，校方還設有「幸福假」，有老師開玩笑說，「幸福假」讓他們有時間替孩子物色另一半。<br />\n<a href=\"https://businessfocus.presslogic.com/2019/01/16/article/89730\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbusinessfocus.presslogic.com%2F2019%2F01%2F16%2Farticle%2F89730&d=muMOnyiyCXy3iUPhFPTZ5b%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=2902f775\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://businessfocus.presslogic.com/2019/01/16/article/89730</a>"},{"pid":"71ef81d0e72bdce7879d3eeaf9fe5168e5f803a3","tid":988561,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T07:39:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"066109c1f43f1050c39c7cf03d9e9df2a1ae74a1","tid":988561,"uid":62011,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T07:40:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">符合條件的老師每月可以上網申請兩次「戀愛假」，每次不超過半日  </span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 半日，返屋企訓啦"}]}